  "text": "There is growing evidence that difficulties performing some activities of daily living (ADL) might be present in mild cognitive impairment (MCI) [CITATION_1] . In 2011, a new classification of MCI was proposed, namely, \"MCI due to Alzheimer's disease\" 2 .",
